Automated de novo assembly of Oxford Nanopore (MinION) & Illumina HiSeq reads with Flye ver. 2.9.1. Assembly polishing with Racoon (ON reads) and
Pilon.

usage: python Flye_assbly_polish.py

require BWA, minimap2, Pilon, Racoon, Flye

Includes 4 rounds of polishin with Oxford Nanopore reads with Racon and 8 rounds of polishing with Illumina PE reads with Pilon.
